CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1956, pg. A29 reads: "U-M-M-M, Good! - The young man doesn't fool around when they're serving food, especially ice cream, at the youth lyceum conference. That's only for girls.  "Boots" Bray and Beverly Butler wrestle with the ice cream wrapper during the banquet. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group of young men and women, including "Boots" Bray and Beverly Butler seated in foreground next to young man eating ice cream bar, seated at banquet tables in Centre Avenue YMCA, for youth lyceum conference
